Vector Icons Roundup

A side-by-side comparison between popular icon fonts.

  • tagliala/vectoriconsroundup
  • @gtagliala

Icon sets

Font Awesome 4.7.0

Follow @fontawesome

Glyphicons

Follow @getbootstrap

Foundation Icon Fonts 3.0

Follow @ZURB

Ionicons 2.0.1

Follow @Ionicframework

Material Design Icons 1.8.36

Follow @Templarian

Elusive-Icons 2.0.0

Follow @reduxframework

Built-in Bulleted Lists
Built-in Rotation and Flipping
Built-in Stacked Icons
Built-in Animated Spinner 5 5
  • 1. Glyphicons Halflings are normally not available for free, but an arrangement between Bootstrap and the Glyphicons creator have made this possible at no cost to you as developers. As a thank you, we ask you to include an optional link back to Glyphicons whenever practical
  • 2. Bootstrap's default font size
  • 3. Except for brand icons and barcode icon
  • 4. Same width is available by adding fa-fw class
  • 5. CPU intensive feature and the animation is not smooth (because of browser support)
  • 6. No woff2 support
  • 7. Dropped in the upcoming Bootstrap 4
